creator: Edwin Arlington Robinson
description:
LibriVox recording of Captain Craig: A Book of Poems by Edwin Arlington Robinson.
Read in English by Subhash Chander; Layla Montipay; Sonia; Kaytlin Rose; George Tau; John-Paul Nelson; Ross Klatte; Amber Jewels; Ryan Finch
This is a volume of narrative poems by Edwin Arlington Robinson. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
